MaXed Stacks Window Manager for X11
===================================

A simpler alternative for https://github.com/tleino/cocowm by the same
author.

WORK IN PROGRESS!

Default key bindings
====================

Stacks
------

F1		Add window stack
F2		Remove window stack
LeftWindows	Select stack on the left
RightWindows	Select stack on the right

Client menu
-----------

Menu		Open menu, focus next item in menu list
Up		Focus previous item in menu list
Down		Focus next item in menu list
Left		Move selected item to a stack on the left side
Right		Move selected item to a stack on the right side
Enter		Select menu item and close menu
Esc		Close menu

Build
=====

./configure ~
make
make install

Dependencies
============

- Practically none on a standard Unix/Linux system that uses
  X11 Window System.
